### Performance & Maintenance

#### Generation Performance
- Target: < 30 seconds for full library (30+ components)
- Incremental: Only changed components processed
- Memory: < 50MB during generation

#### Quality Monitoring
- Coverage: 100% of exported components documented
- Accuracy: Props match TypeScript definitions
- Freshness: Documentation updated with each component change
- Validation: Automated quality checks

#### Maintenance Tasks
- [ ] Review and update documentation templates quarterly
- [ ] Monitor generation performance and optimize as needed
- [ ] Update Confluence integration when available
- [ ] Audit documentation completeness annually

